</p></sec></sec></body><back><glossary><title>Abbreviations</title><def-list><def-item><term>BPS</term><def><p>Bangladesh, Pakistan, Sri Lanka</p></def></def-item><def-item><term>CHW</term><def><p>Community health worker</p></def></def-item><def-item><term>COBRA</term><def><p>Control of Blood Pressure and Risk Attenuation</p></def></def-item><def-item><term>CVD</term><def><p>Cardiovascular disease</p></def></def-item><def-item><term>GP</term><def><p>General practitioner</p></def></def-item><def-item><term>HHE</term><def><p>Home health education</p></def></def-item><def-item><term>MCI</term><def><p>Multicomponent intervention</p></def></def-item><def-item><term>SPIRIT</term><def><p>Standard Protocol Items: Recommendations for Interventional Trials</p></def></def-item></def-list></glossary><fn-group><fn><p><bold>Electronic supplementary material</bold></p><p>The online version of this article (doi:10.1186/s13063-017-2018-0) contains supplementary material, which is available to authorized users.</p></fn></fn-group><ack><title>Acknowledgements</title><p>We would like to acknowledge the members of the Trial Steering Committee and Data Safety and Monitoring Board.</p><p>
